{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a6c015a6d0","title":"接受丹麦驻华公使格瑞杰生呈递国书时的答词","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"9012f616d3","index":0,"year":1953,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"a6c015a6d0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji33","name":"毛泽东全集第33卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/33-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji33":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0975321745","type":"title","text":"接受丹麦驻华公便格瑞杰生呈递国书时的答词","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"},{"id":"df0bdfcdcc","type":"paragraph","text":"公使先生：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"},{"id":"45980e18c7","type":"paragraph","text":"我高兴地接受图下所呈递的丹麦国王隆下的国书，并对您的祝贺表示感谢。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"},{"id":"a0b75b3c3e","type":"paragraph","text":"中国人民对于中、丹两国人民间商业及文化关系的发展，甚为重视，并相信这种关系的发展对于促进两国人民友谊，以及维护世界和平是有帮助的。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"},{"id":"e51b11e748","type":"paragraph","text":"我欢迎图下出任丹麦王国驻中华人民共和国的特命全权公便，并愿对贵公使旨在加强贵我两国友好关系的工作予以协助。","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"},{"id":"60dec7560f","type":"paragraph","text":"谨祝贵国国家繁荣，人民兴旺，并祝贵国国王隆下健康。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0"}],"page":{"id":"22737242d8","publicationId":"maoquanji33","articleId":"a6c015a6d0","start":474,"end":474}}}},"__N_SSG":true}